# ============================================
# SECURITY CHECKLIST
# ============================================
# Before deploying to production, ensure:
# ✓ All passwords are strong and randomly generated
# ✓ JWT_SECRET is at least 32 characters
# ✓ AWS credentials have minimal required permissions (S3 only)
# ✓ ALLOWED_ORIGINS matches your actual domain/IP
# ✓ This .env file is NEVER committed to Git
# ✓ .env has restricted permissions: chmod 600 .env
